# to [[perceive]], to [[discern]], to find out, to [[learn]]

===Verb II===
'''{{ARchar|علم}}''' {{IPAchar|(ʕállama)}}

# to [[teach]], to [[instruct]], to [[train]], to [[educate]]
# to [[designate]], to [[mark]], to [[earmark]]

===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|علم}}''' {{IPAchar|(ʕelm)}} {{m}}, {{ARchar|[[علوم]]}} {{IPAchar|(ʕulūm)}} {{p}}

